{"tid":638784,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：太古海光街便當","createTime":"2018-04-23T04:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T00:39:57.000Z","uid":181719,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"00e521bb633f59200ba8a71fb72928fbc77046c1","tid":638784,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"有晚放工冇乜胃口嘅，行過海光街見到一間賣便當嘅，70蚊有找，仲有1001張堂食位，咁就入左去包場豪一豪。<br />\n<br />\n嗌咗一個汁燒豚肉便當，一食舊豚肉，竟然係咕嚕肉嘅味道黎，唔怪得冇寫係咩汁燒啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/122054_9483a0c356f014cf20d8a4575dfae2d7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F122054_9483a0c356f014cf20d8a4575dfae2d7.jpeg&h=d9bae96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/122125_586cbbfbe8eea99563725f4e17843f07.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F122125_586cbbfbe8eea99563725f4e17843f07.jpeg&h=b6acfa8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之但係咕嚕肉其實我係唔反感嘅，而且食得出佢係即整，大家都知咕嚕肉如果唔係即整，啲汁係會整腍哂肉外面嘅炸皮，但呢度嘅汁燒豚肉，食落仲係脆脆地口。（特寫一張見到脆皮嘅咕嚕肉，如果睇到唔覺得脆，只係我影得唔好）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/122143_999bb2464a47d92bb34c4a694da85479.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F122143_999bb2464a47d92bb34c4a694da85479.jpeg&h=e99d593d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻流心蛋就唔太得，個人比較喜歡蛋白有少少醬油味，但呢半隻完全冇。<br />\n<br />\n炒野菜係炒過，亦都有少少牛油味吊下，但都係偏淡，同埋唔係即炒，已經冇哂鑊氣，只有微温。<br />\n<br />\n飯係五穀果類，係健康嘅，個感覺。同埋叫咗加飯都只係僅僅夠飽。<br />\n<br />\n總括黎講除咗主菜有驚喜之外，其他野一般貨色，但係呢區黎講價錢唔算貴，堂食仲送烏龍茶。"},{"pid":"88679554c16a4c65deebdac9962b3e5ff2637330","tid":638784,"uid":39785,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"70 蚊。。。"},{"pid":"a458467e7dd4e5ed1f8f6ebbc1d2ca9bdff4fc33","tid":638784,"uid":181719,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"88679554c16a4c65deebdac9962b3e5ff2637330","tid":638784,"uid":39785,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"70 蚊。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:14:34.000Z","msg":"其他地方算好貴，太古正常啦"},{"pid":"fa0542b33939215eaabde3e48a6c0c77f0443fb7","tid":638784,"uid":170979,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"行過兩步去食aeon雙餸飯啦 平一半 多樣餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57085d74c7a6110c6c311144a3f8fbadbca391de","tid":638784,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"附帶一題<br />\n隔離賣燒味果間D叉燒好正"},{"pid":"5a404916a586f35476d49abf37033567a9c9664e","tid":638784,"uid":181719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fa0542b33939215eaabde3e48a6c0c77f0443fb7","tid":638784,"uid":170979,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"行過兩步去食aeon雙餸飯啦 平一半 多樣餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"食評：aeon雙餸飯<br />\n預撚咗頹，算係抵食<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b36277f4084acc54f7e6ce08bfc72410e197bd","tid":638784,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57085d74c7a6110c6c311144a3f8fbadbca391de","tid":638784,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"附帶一題<br />\n隔離賣燒味果間D叉燒好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"下次經過試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83224a8e6b2ff76ced951747a56e39686dd3b925","tid":638784,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯 但係70有d貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f322c769207b6c8cc3bf8b